{"tid":1750121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大留守者：部分人不願意進食、驚恐及失去言語能力","createTime":"2019-11-24T09:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T10:29:09.000Z","uid":270126,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fc0c9469dd111ef98aa8d1cb177ec3364695532b","tid":1750121,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:15:21.000Z","msg":"理大留守者今日被困第八日，兩名代表今日見記者，他們認為他們是被警方非法禁錮，部分人身體及精神狀態非常虛弱，包括不願意進食、不欲見任何人及驚恐等，形容是人道災難，促警方盡快撤除圍堵。<br />\n有社工及醫護曾接觸部分被圍堵的留守者，指他們<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">部分不願意進食、不希望見人及長期有驚恐，並出現焦慮甚至失去言語能力，忘記今日是何日，形容已對留守者造成嚴重心理創傷，是國際人道災難。</span></span><br />\n他們無法評估仍留在校園的留守者確實數字，指約30人，但未知準確數字，「佢地都匿埋曬。」<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對於目前留守者的飲食安排，他們指「實在太驚出邊既人，好大戒心」，大部分已不會於校園游走。他們指留守者對警方有極大恐懼，甚至擔心一離開校園的人身安全，促警方盡快撤除圍堵，「否則匿埋既人可能永遠都唔會出嚟。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日是區議會選舉，他們指今日是反送中後第一次變相公投，呼籲市民投票，並指被圍堵的校園的人「都好想出嚟投票」，行使公民權利，對此感到非常慣怒，認為他們的人身自由被限制於校園。<br />\n他們呼籲理大校方盡快與被困的市民及學生進一步接觸，及處理校園內的困境。他們批評理大校董會主席林大輝，日前到訪理大時未有理會留守的「廚房佬」，促校方高層更加積極及主動。<br />\n至於目前校內物資問題，他們指不少物資包括食水已受催淚彈感染，長期食用對留守者身體欠佳。<br />\n記者：鄧佳明<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2D9w5iL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2D9w5iL&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=f5ee6763\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2D9w5iL</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外， <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">劉夢熊都入過去</span></span><br />\n【前政協劉夢熊昨晚入理大 帶走一名20歲學生】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/33cgM3G\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33cgM3G&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=35cf1299\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33cgM3G</a>"},{"pid":"17927b6676b0a6a37f44b4de9c354058f07c0b85","tid":1750121,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:16:16.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6cf742a7d20c183da6caed98cc8f04dbaee315","tid":1750121,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"喺咪咁快就唔記得手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa6013cf6ac34166b00845e5b788b4f563edd2f","tid":1750121,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"手足arrrrrr"},{"pid":"02c64de18e4e4646c9fd904cfc0d60d954db88e8","tid":1750121,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:17:21.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"73b740fd5f1b4fb7cf408f889ee34f86ad610a63","tid":1750121,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:17:55.000Z","msg":"推唔到都推 2/10"},{"pid":"41125ac8c0740e5a3276b7a58124f625118b9644","tid":1750121,"uid":126108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d5c362f611f6ebf8bc18a53fa8cd538cb9526d","tid":1750121,"uid":333470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:19:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7801cdbba1ee3139ffe5f7a34c394eadbcfd616a","tid":1750121,"uid":333470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:19:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid